channel.title: Pi adding the red fence things. [no-ip problem, mabey you could help]
channel.description:
hey guys i had my server up last night running fine people were able to connect, i turned it off this morning compiled and re ran it again and now it's not port forwarding. i checked it was port forwards on my ip, no-ip has all ticks i refreshed in a few times, my server is running fine!, can someone please help me please.! i don't know if something happened to do with the storm i don't know :{ please help. i put my port into canyouseeme.org with both my server and no-ip running and it gave me this error.
[code] Error: I could not see your service on **.****.**** on port (43594) Reason: No route to host [/code]
